{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":635,"text":"It is a dream of mankind\nto fly like a bird."},{"time":4906,"text":"Birds are very agile."},{"time":7000,"text":"They fly, not with rotating components,"},{"time":10358,"text":"so they fly only by flapping their wings."},{"time":13763,"text":"So we looked at the birds,"},{"time":16000,"text":"and we tried to make a model\nthat is powerful, ultralight,"},{"time":22367,"text":"and it must have excellent\naerodynamic qualities"},{"time":26405,"text":"that would fly by its own\nand only by flapping its wings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31140,"text":"So what would be better than to use\nthe herring gull, in its freedom,"},{"time":36000,"text":"circling and swooping over the sea,"},{"time":38338,"text":"and to use this as a role model?"},{"time":41677,"text":"So we bring a team together."},{"time":43661,"text":"There are generalists and also specialists\nin the field of aerodynamics,"},{"time":48765,"text":"in the field of building gliders."},{"time":51329,"text":"And the task was to build\nan ultralight indoor-flying model"},{"time":56726,"text":"that is able to fly over your heads."},{"time":59927,"text":"So be careful later on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62485,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":64817,"text":"And this was one issue:"},{"time":66285,"text":"to build it that lightweight"},{"time":68001,"text":"that no one would be hurt if it fell down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":73388,"text":"So why do we do all this?"},{"time":75364,"text":"We are a company\nin the field of automation,"},{"time":78311,"text":"and we'd like to do\nvery lightweight structures"},{"time":81000,"text":"because that's energy efficient,"},{"time":83763,"text":"and we'd like to learn more\nabout pneumatics and air flow phenomena."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89851,"text":"So I now would like you\nto put your seat belts on"},{"time":94302,"text":"and put your hats on."},{"time":96539,"text":"So maybe we'll try it once --"},{"time":99639,"text":"to fly a SmartBird."}]},{"cues":[{"time":101143,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102195,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":118628,"text":"(Cheers)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":119898,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":134068,"text":"(Applause ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":156008,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":172445,"text":"So we can now look at the SmartBird."},{"time":177824,"text":"So here is one without a skin."},{"time":180330,"text":"We have a wingspan of about two meters."},{"time":183565,"text":"The length is one meter and six,"},{"time":186000,"text":"and the weight is only 450 grams."},{"time":190793,"text":"And it is all out of carbon fiber."},{"time":194000,"text":"In the middle we have a motor,"},{"time":196483,"text":"and we also have a gear in it,"},{"time":200000,"text":"and we use the gear\nto transfer the circulation of the motor."},{"time":205639,"text":"So within the motor,\nwe have three Hall sensors,"},{"time":208849,"text":"so we know exactly where the wing is."},{"time":214450,"text":"And if we now beat up and down --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":217475,"text":"(Mechanical sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":221436,"text":"We have the possibility\nto fly like a bird."},{"time":225523,"text":"So if you go down, you have\nthe large area of propulsion,"},{"time":229165,"text":"and if you go up,"},{"time":232276,"text":"the wings are not that large,"},{"time":235000,"text":"and it is easier to get up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":239869,"text":"So, the next thing we did,"},{"time":242940,"text":"or the challenges we did,"},{"time":244737,"text":"was to coordinate this movement."},{"time":247777,"text":"We have to turn it, go up and go down."},{"time":250990,"text":"We have a split wing."},{"time":252550,"text":"With the split wing,"},{"time":254000,"text":"we get the lift at the upper wing,"},{"time":257000,"text":"and we get the propulsion\nat the lower wing."},{"time":260238,"text":"Also, we see how we measure\nthe aerodynamic efficiency."},{"time":265480,"text":"We had knowledge\nabout the electromechanical efficiency"},{"time":269734,"text":"and then we can calculate\nthe aerodynamic efficiency."},{"time":273716,"text":"So therefore, it rises up\nfrom passive torsion to active torsion,"},{"time":279060,"text":"from 30 percent up to 80 percent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282321,"text":"Next thing we have to do,"},{"time":284204,"text":"we have to control and regulate\nthe whole structure."},{"time":288329,"text":"Only if you control and regulate it,"},{"time":290924,"text":"you will get that aerodynamic efficiency."},{"time":294241,"text":"So the overall consumption of energy"},{"time":297352,"text":"is about 25 watts at takeoff"},{"time":300580,"text":"and 16 to 18 watts in flight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304136,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":305169,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":311774,"text":"Bruno Giussani: Markus,\nwe should fly it once more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314346,"text":"Markus Fischer: Yeah, sure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":315775,"text":"(Audience) Yeah!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":316867,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":338123,"text":"(Gasps)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":346809,"text":"(Cheers)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":348627,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}